クラス JavaDeclarationConverter

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.jdt.internal.compiler.ASTVisitor
ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.ast.java.JavaDeclarationConverter
public class JavaDeclarationConverter
extends org.eclipse.jdt.internal.compiler.ASTVisitor
Visitor to generate an intermediate tree (general, rooted, labeled, valued tree) out of a field, class, or method declaration.
作成者:
Beat Fluri
